scene.message:
Yukino: Who is that woman?{nl}
Hanging a camera around{nl}
her neck like that.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: A weird one,{nl}
that Mariko woman.{waitkey}{clearbox}Like Kuroori, I just don't{nl}
get people who are into{nl}
the occult.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What is that woman?{nl}
She doesn't seem to be{nl}
a student of our school.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That Mariko woman is{nl}
truly enjoying this whole{nl}
situation, isn't she.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: That's the uniform of{nl}
"Yamagumo Private High,"{nl}
famous for its free spirit.{waitkey}{clearbox}She's quite a cutie, isn't{nl}
she! Who is she, I wonder?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Maybe I'll go{nl}
adventuring the tower with{nl}
Mariko-chan...{waitkey}{ret}

Mariko: Hm? Was there{nl}
something in that chest?{waitkey}{clearbox}Yeah, this "Mirror Shard"{nl}
was inside! I feel a strong{nl}
spiritual power from this{waitkey}mirror.{waitkey}{clearbox}It must be a psychic item{nl}
with great hidden power,{nl}
surely.{waitkey}{clearbox}Hm? You want this?{nl}
Hmm...{waitkey}{clearbox}5000 yen! How's that? I'm{nl}
the one who found it first,{nl}
so... not too pricey, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Mariko: Thanks!{nl}
I've been snapping photos{nl}
like crazy since entering{waitkey}this tower, so film's pricey.{waitkey}{clearbox}Alright! Now I can buy{nl}
more film!{waitkey}{ret}

Mariko: Hmm, oh, I see.{nl}
You don't want it, huh.{waitkey}{clearbox}Then I'll send it to{nl}
"Lemuria" to have it{nl}
appraised!{waitkey}{ret}

Mariko: Hey! You don't even{nl}
have 5000 yen?{nl}
Sheesh, how pathetic!{waitkey}{clearbox}Then you can come with me{nl}
and work off 5000 yen's{nl}
worth.{waitkey}{clearbox}Hm? No?{waitkey}{clearbox}Then pay up the full{nl}
5000 yen, right now!{waitkey}{ret}

Mariko: Honestly, I'm so{nl}
lucky!{waitkey}{clearbox}You couldn't get photos of{nl}
the afterlife in a whole{nl}
lifetime!{waitkey}{clearbox}When I get back, I've got to{nl}
submit these photos to{nl}
"Fortean World"!{waitkey}{ret}

???: Oh, hello!{nl}
Nice to meet you!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm Mariko Yabe of the{nl}
"Yamagumo Private High School{nl}
Paranormal Club"! Nice to{waitkey}meet you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Though it's an unofficial club{nl}
where I'm both president and{nl}
sole member!{waitkey}{clearbox}My homeroom teacher won't{nl}
approve the club just because{nl}
he says it's "lame"!{waitkey}{clearbox}So today I came to meet my{nl}
comrade Kuroori, but...{nl}
never{wait_fr:30} did I think...{waitkey}{clearbox}I'd get caught up in such an{nl}
amazing paranormal event!{nl}
I'm, like, super lucky!{waitkey}{clearbox}I've been snapping photos like{nl}
crazy! And I'll submit these{nl}
demon photos to a magazine!{waitkey}{clearbox}Then! Maybe the teacher will{nl}
approve the club after all!{nl}
Alright! I'll do my best!{waitkey}{ret}
